                (156, 1, 'Price Factor Offset', '<p>This product is priced at $10.00</p><p>The attributes are priced using the Price Factor and Price Factor Offset</p><p>Red is $10 ($0)<br />Yellow is $20 ($10)<br />Green is $30 ($20)</p><p>The Price Factor Offset is set to 1 to take out the price of the Product Price then make the total price $10 + the price factor * $10 - price factor offset * $10 for the attributes.</p>', ''),
